node.text:
Holy smokes, the first ever @guysrestaurantreboot presented by @lendingtree was incredible!

Thank you again to all of our amazing chefs including @chefjoseandres @marcuscooks @catcora @guarnaschelli @shaq @gronk @adrianalima @wale @kanebrown_music and dynamite musicians @olddominionmusic and @diplo who joined us! 

Best of all we gave away $300,000 via The Help Rebuild Restaurants Grant to a remarkable group of restaurant owners and entrepreneurs. Special thanks to our presenting partner @lendingtree who has been helping restaurants and small businesses throughout the pandemic. To learn more visit LendingTree.com/reboot

node.text:
The moment you've all been waiting for, it's official! Head to the @santospirit website now to buy yours and have a taste of what we think is the world's finest Reposado.

The Santo Family is on the road again too, celebrating the official launch of Santo Reposado. Follow along on @santospirit Instagram Stories and get a behind the scenes look at the action!

node.text:
I’ve seen a ton of great videos, but I gotta hear from more of Flavortown’s citizens before @hunterfieri and I crown a winner. Get your video posted by 11:59pm this Sunday (8/23) for your chance to win!

And don’t forget to hashtag #DDDfavorite and tag @foodnetwork & @citizenpictures so we can find those posts, I gotta hear from all of ya!

node.text:
There are no ifs, ands or buts about it. Lunchtime is the best part of the school day and a sandwich on soft and fluffy @kingshawaiian Mini-Sub Rolls makes for the most dynamite lunch there is.

But millions of kids are struggling to get the food they need to learn and thrive. That’s why @kingshawaiian is proud to partner with @nokidhungry to launch “Share a post, help feed kids” – and we need YOUR help!

Beginning today, for every public social media post you share using #KHShareOurBread, they’ll
donate $5, which can help provide up to fifty meals to kids in need. Check out the link in my bio for more info. #ad

🍞🍞🍞
